WEBVTT

00:01.320 --> 00:02.680
The man with your sister,

00:02.719 --> 00:04.440
I saw him with a bloody knife.

00:05.720 --> 00:07.320
I cannot say it any clearer,

00:07.400 --> 00:08.320
this man is a killer!

00:08.400 --> 00:10.000
So am I. Be silent

00:10.080 --> 00:11.560
or your lovely daughter hangs.

00:11.640 --> 00:13.720
There's a little Quiggy
growing inside me.

00:13.800 --> 00:15.880
You've taken my family from me.

00:15.960 --> 00:17.800
I want you to lose
your family too.

00:19.000 --> 00:20.600
I hate you.

00:21.640 --> 00:23.000
I'm taking her home.

00:23.120 --> 00:24.800
My secret is a child.

00:26.160 --> 00:27.160
She is his.

00:27.280 --> 00:28.440
I want news of Amelia.

00:28.480 --> 00:29.920
Take care of things for me.

00:30.000 --> 00:32.200
I confess to the murder
of Sir George Howard.

00:32.280 --> 00:34.000
I have the Wells girl
as my surety.

00:34.040 --> 00:36.120
And witnesses can perish.

00:36.240 --> 00:37.760
Tell Charlotte
I've gone to bed.

00:37.880 --> 00:39.400
I can tell you
the name of the man

00:39.520 --> 00:40.600
who stabbed Amelia.

00:40.640 --> 00:42.080
It is Lord Fallon.

